{"tid":1798851,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"除良安暴、儆善懲忠 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T13:58:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"212156cad6354d5b82e750475f14d47e935623cd","tid":1798851,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191226/20831545/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831545%2F&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=01f0b350\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831545%2F&h=d8488087\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191226/20831545/</a><br />\n<br />\n除良安暴、儆善懲忠 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191226/large/1577257595_b006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191226%2Flarge%2F1577257595_b006.jpg&h=920d2503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n令香港人心惶惶的搶劫潮來了！以前每年12月聖誕節至翌年農曆新年的消費旺季也是搶劫旺季，不過警方高調巡邏進行「冬防」行動，防止罪案發生，亦盡快追捕歹人，市民也放心一點。<br />\n<br />\n今年，各區已是「無警時份」，大家已很久沒見到行咇，似乎沒有警察夠膽不蒙面不武裝不集體行動，光明正大執行男子漢大丈夫職務，沒有！接獲投訴根本不理，報警並無實效。<br />\n<br />\n近日市區發生多宗劫案，鐵鎚6人幫劫金行100萬、硬物扑頭搶去20萬、持槍破玻璃掠走價值約60萬之手錶、持刀賊掠走約200萬元金飾、5、6名賊匪當街搶去逾千萬現金、的士司機和四驅車車主遇劫&hellip;&hellip;對比去年同期，罪案飆升逾40%。還有大量內地殘丐湧至。<br />\n<br />\n警力哪兒去了？主力應付示威活動及警民衝突：無差別挑釁生事狂發山埃催淚彈、真槍指嚇阿婆、毒打學生及街坊、插贓嫁禍、2小童在元朗遊樂場玩耍時被約10名警員包圍指罵表示懷疑小童犯罪、槍擊路人滿地鮮血&hellip;&hellip;不敢落單，聯群結隊嬉皮笑臉高喊5大訴求：「吃喝玩樂玩！」（前「玩」與後「玩」有何不同？），禍民OT耗費公帑近10億。<br />\n<br />\n市民一直誤會其使命是「除暴安良，儆惡懲奸」──錯了，今時今日黑警是「除良安暴，儆善懲忠」。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f4fd6992573b1ba1271be08dc998fa94ca292069","tid":1798851,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"d50584651b7f8bfbb2a58960a605a1cc71ecbca1","tid":1798851,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"【第拾玖期牆紙】毋懼強權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=b1ed7bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqcF6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqcF6Fe.jpg&h=44c58009&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}